PRIVACY POLICY
Jyotish Vishwakosh – Astrology
Effective Date: December 5, 2025
This Privacy Policy explains how Jyotish Vishwakosh – Astrology (“we”, “us”, “our”) collects, uses, and
protects your information when you use our mobile application (the “App”). By using the App, you agree
to the practices described here.
1. Information We Collect
We only collect information you provide directly. We do NOT collect location data, IP addresses, device
identifiers, device model, operating system details, analytics data, crash logs, or voice notes.
Information you may provide:
• Name
• Email address
• Phone number
• Birth details (date, time, place)
• Chat messages with astrologers
• Feedback, ratings
• Payment-related information processed through Razorpay (we do not store full card or banking
details)
2. How We Use Your Information
We use the information you voluntarily provide to:
• Offer astrology consultations
• Enable chat features with astrologers
• Process secure payments through Razorpay
• Manage your account
• Provide customer support
• Improve the quality of our services
We do not use your information for advertising, profiling, or selling to third parties.
3. Sharing and Disclosure
We do not sell or rent your personal information.
We may share limited information with:
• Razorpay (payment processing)
• Astrologers (only information required for consultation)
We may also disclose information if required by law.
4. Data Retention and Deletion
We retain your information only as long as necessary to:
• Provide services
• Comply with legal obligations
You may request account or data deletion via email:
bhupendrapandey29@gmail.com
5. Security
We implement reasonable safeguards to protect the information you provide. However, no digital
platform is 100% secure.
6. Children’s Privacy
The App is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children without
parental consent.
7. Your Rights
You may request:
• Access to your data
• Correction
• Deletion
• Withdrawal of consent
Contact: bhupendrapandey29@gmail.com
8. Third-Party Links
If the App contains third■party links, those sites have separate privacy practices.
9. Policy Updates
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. The updated version will include a revised Effective
Date.
10. Contact Us
If you have questions regarding this policy, contact:
Email: bhupendrapandey29@gmail.com
Address: Arera Colony, Madhya Pradesh, India
Publisher: Jyotish Vishwakosh – Astrology
Last Updated: December 5, 2025
